y:Actresses from Vancouver]]\n[[Category:Canadian child actresses]]\n[[Category:Canadian emigrants to the United States]]\n[[Category:Canadian film actresses]]\n[[Category:Canadian musical theatre actresses]]\n[[Category:Canadian soap opera actresses]]\n[[Category:Canadian television actresses]]\n", "name_user": "JJMC89", "label": "safe", "comment": "Removing link(s):Wikipedia:Articles for deletion/Simple Little Livesclosed as delete (XFDcloser)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natalie_Hall"}
{"title_page": "Ismael Cruz C\u00f3rdova", "text_new": "{{short description|Puerto Rican television, stage and film actor}}\n{{BLP sources|date=November 2013}}\n{{Spanish name|Cruz|Cordova}}\n{{Infobox person\n|name=Ismael Cruz C\u00f3rdova\n|birth_date={{birth date and age|1987|4|7}}\n|birth_place=[[Aguas Buenas, Puerto Rico]]\n|occupation=Actor\n|yearsactive=2003-present\n}}\n'''Ismael Enrique Cruz C\u00f3rdova''' (born April 7, 1987) is a Puerto Rican [[television]], stage and [[film]] actor who gained national attention playing Mando on ''[[Sesame Street]]''. Ismael also had a successful role in the Showtime original series ''[[Ray Donovan]]'',<ref>{{cite web|author=Brandon K. Thorp |url=http://www.browardpalmbeach.com/2010-03-11/culture/a-farewell-to-grit/ |title=A Farewell to Grit - Page 1 - Arts - Fort Lauderdale and Palm Beach - New Times Broward-Palm Beach |publisher=Browardpalmbeach.com |date=2010-03-11 |accessdate=2014-02-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/141935-Political-Subversities-to-Play-Joes-Pub-Casting-Announced |title=Political Subversities to Play Joe's Pub; Casting Announced |publisher=Playbill.com |date=2010-08-10 |accessdate=2014-02-03}}</ref><ref>[http://elperiodicousa.com/noticiashispanicprwire/19338/teatro-latea-presenta-off-broadway-una-nueva-y-provocativa-obra-dominicana/ ]{{dead link|date=February 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/09/01/arts/television/a-chameleon-onstage-and-on-tv.html|title=A Chameleon Onstage and on TV|newspaper=[[The New York Times]]|accessdate=2014-02-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/05/14/ismael-cruz-cordova-sesame-street_n_3272247.html |title=Ismael Cruz Cordova Talks Becoming Mando For 'Sesame Street': 'It's A Big Honor, A Great Responsibility' |publisher=Huffingtonpost.com |date=2013-05-14 |accessdate=2014-02-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Puga |first=Kristina |url=http://nbclatino.com/2013/09/19/mando-debuts-today-on-sesame-street/ |title=\"Mando\" debuts on \"Sesame Street\" |publisher=Nbclatino.com |date=2013-09-19 |accessdate=2014-02-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.klru.org/blog/tag/ismael-cruz-cordova/ |title=Ismael Cruz C\u00f3rdova &#124; KLRU-TV, Austin PBS |publisher=Klru.org |date=2013-08-30 |accessdate=2014-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203022532/http://www.klru.org/blog/tag/ismael-cruz-cordova/ |archive-date=2013-12-03 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sefijaonline.com/ismael-cruz-cordova-the-newest-latino-on-sesame-street/ |title=Ismael Cruz C\u00f3rdova: the Newest Latino on \"Sesame Street\" \u00bb Se Fija! |publisher=Sefijaonline.com |date=2013-11-04 |accessdate=2014-02-03}}</ref> and in the third season of ''[[Berlin Station (TV series)|Berlin Station]]'', as Rafael Torres, an [[Special Activities Center|SOG]] operative. In early 2020 it was revealed that he had been cast in an undisclosed role in ''[[Adaptations of The Lord of the Rings|The Lord Of The Rings]]'' on [[Prime Video|Amazon Prime]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/01/lord-of-the-rings-amazon-studios-sets-series-cast-tca-1202830413/|title=\u2018The Lord Of The Rings\u2019: Amazon Studios Sets Series Cast \u2013 TCA|last=D'Aless|first=Anthony|last2=ro|date=2020-01-14|website=Deadline|access-date=2020-03-10}}</ref>\n\n==Filmography==\n===Film===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n!scope=\"col\"|Title\n!scope=\"col\"|Year\n!scope=\"col\"|Role\n!scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\"|Notes\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''Stray Bullet''\n|2003\n|Gatillo\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''White Alligator''\n|2012\n|Alejandro\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''La Edwin''\n|2012\n|Johnny\n|Short film\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''Chaser''\n|2013\n|Ian\n|Short film\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''La Loteria''\n|2014\n|Augusto\n|Short film\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''[[In the Blood (2014 film)|In the Blood]]''\n|2014\n|Manny<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latina.com/entertainment/buzz/ismael-cruz-cordova-exclusive-interview|title=EXCLUSIVE: Ismael Cruz Cordova on In the Blood, Danny Trejo and More|date=2013-10-03|publisher=Latina.com|accessdate=2014-02-03}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''The Golden Record''\n|2014\n|Eli\n|Short film\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''Simple Little Lives''\n|2015\n|Henry\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''[[Exposed (2016 film)|Exposed]]\n|2016\n|{{sort|De La Cruz|Jose De La Cruz}}\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''The Pastor''\n|2016\n|Netto\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''[[Billy Lynn's Long Halftime Walk (film)|Billy Lynn's Long Halftime Walk]]''\n|2016\n|Holliday\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''[[Mary Queen of Scots (2018 film)|Mary Queen of Scots]]''\n|2018\n|{{sort|Rizzio|David Rizzio}}\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''[[Miss Bala (2019 film)|Miss Bala]]''\n|2019\n|{{sort|Esparza|Lino Esparza}}\n|\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n!scope=\"col\"|Title\n!scope=\"col\"|Year\n!scope=\"col\"|Role\n!scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\"|Notes\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''El Cuerpo del Delito''\n|2005\n|Manny\n|Television film\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''[[The Good Wife]]''\n|2011\n|{{sort|Patrick|Jimmy Patrick}}\n|5 episodes\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''Little Children, Big Challenges''\n|2012\u201313\n|Mando\n|2 episodes\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''[[Sesame Street]]''\n|2013\u201314\n|Mando\n|12 episodes\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''[[Ray Donovan]]''\n|2016\n|{{sort|Campos|Hector Campos}}\n|Recurring role<br />season 4; 10 episodes\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''[[Divorce (TV series)|Divorce]]''\n|2016\n|Clerk\n|Episode: \"Mediation\"\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''Citizen''\n|2016\n|{{sort|Martinez|Chris Martinez}}\n|1 episode\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''[[The Catch (TV series)|The Catch]]''\n|2017\n|The Hammer\n|3 episodes\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''[[Berlin Station (TV series)|Berlin Station]]''\n|2018\n|{{sort|Torres|Rafael Torres}}\n|Main role<br />season 3\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|''[[The Mandalorian]]''\n|2019\n|Qin\n|1 episode\n|-\n!''[[Adaptations of The Lord of the Rings|T